{"tid":1519551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831 和理非一定要出街！唔出，林鄭贏晒","createTime":"2019-08-30T15:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T15:11:19.000Z","uid":279453,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"447d58bc3a3ebbd35755208d7f3dd88c27587e28","tid":1519551,"uid":279453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:08:57.000Z","msg":"雖然知道Ｐ牌冇人理，但我點都要出聲<br />\n<br />\n連登可否搞個投票「建議」行街地點？<br />\n<br />\n如果明日唔出來，林鄭就贏晒！唔好講乜仲有10.1等等<br />\n林鄭驚ger唔係勇武，她最驚係百幾萬和理非代表主流民意，上晒國際新聞（好多謝勇武朋友一直保護和理非，但理性分析我們的勇武vs警方暴力和裝備=雞蛋vs石頭）<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日高調又出黑又出警去打擊我們，拘捕所謂「大台」係因為林鄭已經冇晒橋！只可以大大力恐嚇和理非唔敢出來！<br />\n<br />\n明日如果出現下面的情況我們就輸<br />\n1. 人少，等於香港人屈服於白色恐佈<br />\n2.遍地開花，各區勇士被警方升級暴力極速打擊，犧牲佐前線手足<br />\n3.有人命傷亡，無論係邊一方面的人都會俾機會林鄭將警方暴力合法化！<br />\n<br />\n我們一定要贏，哪怕冇大台，和理非集中一起出來係一兩區「行街」！"},{"pid":"a6014ff785fde871fe27694747549204100592df","tid":1519551,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T15:10:56.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0ogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=404b3c59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouop